Before architectural decisions or a new day's task, MUST read PLAN.md.

- Pydantic for all LLM outputs; parse via llm_parse.py then model_validate_json.
- Agent: classified recovery + per-step verify; NO blind retry loops.
- 10-K: Tier0 BS4 first; forbid summarization; token/header guards in metrics.
- Cost: enforce Circuit Breaker Matrix in cost_tracker (thread-safe; no global float).
- LLM: litellm only; Google primary, OpenRouter fallback once per (tier, call).
- NO bare except Exception for fallback; catch RateLimit/Timeout/5xx explicitly.
- NO fallback if BudgetExceeded; ValidationError: primary retry 1 then fallback once.
- SEC: all requests via edgar_client.py only; SEC_USER_AGENT required; rate limit <=10/s.
- New agent/segment/LLM logic MUST add or update tests/unit or tests/integration.
- Prompt v1→v2: update prompts/ITERATION.md (Failed Path, Resolution, Validation test name).
- Blind Critic: use prompts/v1_blind_critic.txt; negative constraints; JSON only via llm_parse.
- SOP: prompts/sops/*.md via prompt_loader ONLY; recovery.py routes by failure_type — NO skills/ folder; NO agent self-select skill file.
